<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <title>WayTravelTrek</title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <link rel="icon" href="">

    <!-- A単adiendo Bootstrap -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
        integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <!-- A単adiendo normalize.css -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.min.css">

    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/484a0c911a.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    <style type="text/css">
        p{
            font-size: 20px;
        }

        i.fa-facebook-f, i.fa-instagram, i.fa-twitter, i.fa-envelope-open{
            font-size: 40px;
        }

        .enmarcado{
            width: 80px;
            height: 80px;
        }
    </style>

</head>

<body class="container-fluid mt-5">


    <!-- *********************************************************************************************************
                                                INFORMACION DE RESERVA DEL AUTO DE RENTA
    **************************************************************************************************************-->
    <p class="container mt-3">
        Hola, se ha solicitado una nueva reserva. En un per&iacute;odo m&aacute;ximo de 48 horas la solicitud de reserva ser&aacute; respondida. Aqu&iacute; puede ver detalles:
    </p>

    <p class="display-4 container text-success">
        C&oacute;digo de reserva: <span id="codigo">{{reserva.getCodigo}}</span>
    </p>

    <div id="info-reserva-auto" class="container">
        <div class="row row-cols-sm-1 row-col-md-3">
            <!-- INFORMACION DEL CLIENTE -->
            <div id="" class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="container bg-light py-4 my-5 shadow">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-4">Informaci&oacute;n del cliente</h2>
                    <div class="container-fluid border-bottom mb-3">
                        <div class="row row-cols-2">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Nombre</h6>
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Apellido</h6>

                            <span class="small" id="nombre-cliente">{{reserva.getNombre}}</span>
                            <span class="small" id="apellido-cliente">{{reserva.getApellido}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container-fluid border-bottom mb-3">
                        <div class="row row-cols-1">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Email</h6>
                            <span id="email-cliente" class="small">{{reserva.getCorreo}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- INFORMACION DE LA RESERVA DEL AUTO -->
            <div id="" class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="container bg-light py-4 my-5 shadow">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-4">Informaci&oacute;n de la reserva</h2>
                    <div class="container-fluid border-bottom mb-3">
                        <div class="row row-cols-2 mb-3 border-bottom">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Check-in</h6>
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Check-out</h6>

                            <span class="small" id="fecha-recogida">{{reserva.getFechaEntrada|date('d M yy')}}</span>
                            <span class="small" id="hora-recogida">{{reserva.getFechaSalida|date('d M yy')}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row row-cols-2 mt-2">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Habtaciones</h6>
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Adultos</h6>

                            <span class="small" id="fecha-entrega">{{habitaciones}}</span>
                            <span class="small" id="hora-entrega">{{reserva.getAdultos}}</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row row-cols-2 mt-2">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Ni単os</h6>
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Infantes</h6>

                            <span class="small" id="fecha-entrega">{{reserva.getNinos}}</span>
                            <span class="small" id="hora-entrega">{{reserva.getInfantes}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container-fluid border-bottom mb-3">
                        <div class="row row-cols-2">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Per&iacute;odo de reserva</h6>
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Categor&iacute;a habitaci&oacute;n</h6>
                            {% set diferencia = reserva.getFechaEntrada.diff(reserva.getFechaSalida)%}
                            {% set dias = diferencia.days %}
                            <span id="periodo-renta" class="small">{{dias}} d&iacute;as</span>
                            <span id="categoria-auto" class="small">{{hotel.getTipoHab[0].getTipo}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container-fluid border-bottom mb-3">
                        <div class="row row-cols-1">
                            <h6 class="text-muted">Hotel</h6>
                            <span id="car-name" class="small">{{hotel.getNombre}}</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="container-fluid">
                        <div class="row row-cols-1">                    
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- INFORMACION DE PAGO -->
            <div id="" class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="container bg-light py-4 my-5 shadow">
                    <h2 class="h4 mb-4">Informaci&oacute;n de pago</h2>
                    <div class="container-fluid mb-3">
                        <div class="row row-cols-1">
                            <table class="table table-striped table-light table-hover shadow-sm">
                                <thead>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Descripci&oacute;n</th>
                                        <th>Debes pagar</th>
                                    </tr>
                                </thead>
                                <tbody>
                                   
                                     
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Habitaci&oacute;n</td>
                                        <td> 190 USD / noche</td>
                                    </tr>
                                

                                    
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Suplemento</td>
                                        <td>150 USD</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Cantidad de noches</td>
                                        <td>{{dias}}</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <td>Descuento</td>
                                        <td>$0 USD</td>
                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                        <th>Total:</th>
                                        <td>{{precio}}</td>
                                    </tr>
                                </tbody>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <h3>S&iacute;ganos en nuestras redes sociales</h3>
        <p>
            No olvides seguirnos en nuestras redes y conpartir todo nuestro contenido. Estaremos publicando ofertas y promociones. Muchas gracias por elegir WayTravelTrek para planear su viaje.
        </p>
        <div class="row row-cols-4 mb-3 p-4">
            <div class="col-sm-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                <div class="shadow enmarcado rounded d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                <div class="shadow enmarcado rounded d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                <div class="shadow enmarcado rounded d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <a href="#"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                <div class="shadow enmarcado rounded d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                    <a href="https://waytraveltrek.com#subscribirse" target="__blank"><i class="fas fa-envelope-open"></i></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container border-top mt-5">
        <p class="small text-muted pt-4">
            &copy; WayTravelTrek 2020 - 2021 | Todos los derechos reservados
        </p>
    </div>



    <!-- A単adiendo scripts js -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-ho+j7jyWK8fNQe+A12Hb8AhRq26LrZ/JpcUGGOn+Y7RsweNrtN/tE3MoK7ZeZDyx" crossorigin="anonymous">
    </script>

</body>

</html>